		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The only problem with the unofficial opcodes is that <a href="http://nocash.emubase.de/everynes.htm#cpuillegalopcodes" class="postlink">Martin Korth claims they don't always work</a> on certain 6502 based computers.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
